Somebody check out the building.
Two men, check out the building.

01:33:47.371 --> 01:33:49.706
Gotta work in pairs.

01:33:51.375 --> 01:33:53.376
We gotta get in there.

01:34:04.972 --> 01:34:06.973
[Clangs]

01:34:13.898 --> 01:34:16.399
- [Man]
