[Peckem's Voice]
Right on the money as far
as the, uh, census info is concerned.

01:38:18.726 --> 01:38:21.811
3,613 total population.

01:38:25.608 --> 01:38:27.984
Twenty-
Twenty-one hundred survivors.

01:38:29.904 --> 01:38:31.321
