[Man's Voice]
I see no way out of this.

01:40:42.953 --> 01:40:46.372
There's never been-
There's never been a Trixie before.

01:40:46.457 --> 01:40:48.666
In admission, there's nothing about it.

01:40:48.792 --> 01:40:51.711
